title: Fired Benghazi panel staffer ‘never mentioned’ Clinton before Friday, chairman says
text: Rep. Trey Gowdy , chairman of the House committee investigating the 2012 attack on the U.S. Consulate in Banghazi , Libya , Select Committee on Benghazi , Sunday contradicted a former committee staffer who said he was fired for not cooperating
